title: Freckles Comes Home ( 1942) Full Movie Johnny Downs, Gale Storm, Mantan Moreland

sources.title: Freckles Comes Home ( 1942) Full Movie Johnny Downs, Gale Storm, Mantan Moreland
sources.description: College student Freckles returns home from school, and the sheriff accuses him of murder. He is also threatened after meeting a Chicago gangster, and his girlfriend falls in love with a con man.
